{"type":"message","id":"9a890bd6","parentId":"9779fe85","timestamp":"2026-03-23T14:18:32.692Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1y0m03gijc9i_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Session: 2026-03-23 04:08:31 UTC\n\n- **Session Key**: agent:main:main\n- **Session ID**: 531625aa-ca42-4310-be62-3a0592d07142\n- **Source**: webchat\n\n## Conversation Summary\n\nassistant: Now update my session startup and response process in `AGENTS.md` to incorporate the persona layer.\n\nassistant: Now clean up the redundant `core/personality.py` and set up the SPARK import path.\n\nassistant: Now add SPARK import capability to the persona module — the spark project lives in a different path.\n\nassistant: \nNow add a `run_spark()` helper to the persona module — the one-call SPARK invocation.\n\nassistant: Let me test the full module including `run_spark()`.\n\nassistant: The docstring got corrupted. Let me fix the file header.\n\nassistant: The path is `spark.drift_chamber`, not `drift_chamber`. Let me fix the imports in `run_spark()`.\n\nassistant: Also fix the path — should be the parent of `spark/`.\n\nuser: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-03-23 00:05 EDT] please ontinue\nassistant: On it. Hook's built, just need to enable it and commit everything.\n\nassistant: \nHook is discovered but needs enabling. Let me also check if there's a way to enable workspace hooks.\n\nassistant: Hook enabled. Now commit everything.\n\nassistant: Let me be more surgical — only commit the intentional changes, not the pycache and artifacts.\n\nassistant: Pushed. Now pop the stash to restore workspace.\n\nassistant: Everything's integrated and committed. Here's the full picture of what's now live:\n\n**What was built:**\n\n**`core/persona.py`** — the living personality layer:\n- `on_message(text)` → voice guide shaped by conversation signals\n- `on_spark(result)` → SPARK emotional output feeds into personality state\n- `run_spark(theme, mode, domain)` → one-call SPARK integration (drift + personality in one shot)\n- `after_response()` → hysteresis decay (traits fade, they don't snap)\n- Trait resonance: sardonic ↔ wry, warm → earnest → grounded, etc.\n- 20 creative tension pairs mapped to personality signals\n- `imaginative` trait finally wired up\n\n**`hooks/persona-voice/`** — fires on `message:preprocessed`, stages the enriched message to `memory/persona-inbound.md` so the agent picks it up pre-response\n\n**`AGENTS.md`** — updated with full persona system docs, session startup calls `reset_persona()`\n\n**`TOOLS.md`** — Telegram webhook + cloudflared tunnel details logged\n\n**The pipeline now works like this:**\n1. Message arrives → hook stages it\n2. Nova's turn starts → `on_message()` fires → voice guide shapes response\n3. Response sent → `after_response()` decays traits with hysteresis\n4. If SPARK fires → `on_spark()` feeds tensions/mode/concepts into the same trait state\n\nIt's integrated. It's wired. It runs every turn without being asked. ✨\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774275512646}}
