{"type":"message","id":"68224648","parentId":"854f54a3","timestamp":"2026-03-23T14:33:33.708Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zach wants to know how to talk to the Modal Ollama endpoint. Let me test the generate endpoint now to see if it's ready, and also give him the full instructions.\n\nThe endpoint is:\n`https://toxzak-svg--spark-ollama-qwen-generate.modal.run`\n\nIt uses the Ollama API format. The FastAPI endpoint expects `POST /` with a JSON body containing `prompt`, `model`, and optional `options`.\n\nBut wait - the error earlier said `POST /` returns 405 Method Not Allowed and `POST /generate` returns 404. The `/` path is the FastAPI default, and it should be routed to the `generate` method. \n\nI'm seeing 405 on the root path which suggests the routing might not be set up correctly - with `fastapi_endpoint()`, the function name becomes the path, so it should be accessible at `/generate` instead. The fact that `/generate` returned 404 earlier is puzzling, but those logs might be from before the redeploy when the model wasn't even pulled yet. Let me try hitting it again now to see if the new container has the routing configured properly.\n\nActually, I think I see the real issue now - looking at the logs, `POST /` returned 405 Method Not Allowed while `GET /` returned 200. This points to the `generate` function not being properly decorated with the right HTTP method, or the FastAPI endpoint configuration isn't matching what I expected.\n\nBut wait - those logs were from an earlier deployment. The new version with the model pull should be deployed by now. Let me test the actual endpoint to see if it's working now.","thinkingSignature":"e73880783068f9a70b14914977ca4615c4e88715d85169bde6ac0691384a1ec1"},{"type":"text","text":"Let me test if it's ready:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ibdw19ltgglv_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST \"https://toxzak-svg--spark-ollama-qwen-generate.modal.run\" -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"prompt\":\"Say hello in one sentence.\",\"model\":\"qwen2.5:7b\"}' 2>&1","yieldMs":30000,"timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":452,"cacheRead":13714,"cacheWrite":28322,"totalTokens":42531,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774276390066}}
