even available. The issue might be that I need to explicitly specify `method=\"POST\"` in the decorator, or there's a routing problem with how the endpoints are mounted. Let me try switching to `modal.web_endpoint` instead, which is more straightforward for this use case.","thinkingSignature":"730b94c6891bb2ccd0478c03b585407350bf74ed3ee6517b0c780e43750f1fdf"},{"type":"text","text":"The old container is still running. The redeploy updated the *app definition* but the container won't restart until it cold-starts. Let me stop the old one so a new container spins up with the model pull:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sv25ldd0ox2s_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"modal app stop spark-ollama 2>&1","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":32129,"output":547,"cacheRead":13714,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46390,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774276472334}}
