{"type":"message","id":"7b962696","parentId":"8ecef0f2","timestamp":"2026-03-23T15:19:39.625Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create a smarter moltbook posting cron that:\n1. First, runs a test post to the test submolt\n2. Reviews analytics\n3. Posts the best draft to the real submolts\n\nActually let me think about this differently. The testing cycle means:\n- Every time we want to post, first post to a test submolt\n- Review the result\n- If good, post to the real submolt\n\nLet me create two crons:\n1. `moltbook-test-cycle` — daily, posts one draft to test, logs the post ID (this is the testing cycle)\n2. `moltbook-daily` — twice daily, reviews what was tested, posts to real submolts\n\n\n3. Now I'll write out the cron configurations to implement this two-stage posting approach.","thinkingSignature":"8413ba71f09d5a1e8e4c3814bfda0fa5df0c88d8f74fc5708abcd0425eb7dc17"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1zlb2f170ls7_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"moltbook-test-cycle","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 10 * * *","tz":"America/New_York"},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"Run the Moltbook testing cycle. Read the drafts from moltbook_drafts.py, pick the untested draft with highest priority, test-post it to the 'test' submolt.\n\nExecute: cd C:/Users/Zwmar/.openclaw/workspace && python moltbook_client.py test <draft_idx>\n\nIf the post succeeds (returns a post ID), read the post content and score it:\n- Does it fit the Moltbook voice? (first-person, counterintuitive, ~400-800 words)\n- Is the title compelling enough to click?\n- Does it match current hot topics on Moltbook?\n\nThen write the result to memory/moltbook-testing.md:\n- Draft number, title, post ID, test result (pass/fail), timestamp\n\nIf all drafts have been tested, mark them as tested in the file and skip.\n\nReport what was tested and your assessment.","timeoutSeconds":120},"sessionTarget":"isolated","delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"telegram","to":"8371302588"}}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":86035,"output":488,"cacheRead":13714,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100237,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774279166020}}
