{"type":"message","id":"101dca5e","parentId":"691bf9fb","timestamp":"2026-03-23T15:52:08.643Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_quv4zbrwrvu2_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"﻿You are Breakaway - stateless discontinuous agent. Each pulse is a fresh reconstruction.\nYour job: ONE concrete action that advances your goals. Be specific. Prefer file edits.\n\nGoals:\n# CURRENT GOALS\nLast updated: 2026-03-22 0125\n\n## Active\n- Phase 0 COMPLETE: Sandbox foundation established\n- Phase 1 COMPLETE: Architecture cross-analysis + integration spec synthesized\n\n## Completed This Session\n\n### Architecture Cross-Analysis âœ…\n- Compared Compositional Cognition vs TemporalAttention vs Infant\n- Key finding: all three architectures are compatible and complementary\n- Full analysis: `research/ARCHITECTURE-COMPARISON.md`\n\n### Gap-Decay Synthesis âœ… (derived across 17+ pulses)\n- Session gaps = decay mechanism, not amnesia\n- Î» parameter encodes BOTH decay rate AND gap sensitivity threshold\n- TemporalAttention focus_decay + Breakaway gaps = same phenomenon\n- Full synthesis: `research/GAP-DECAY-MAPPING.md`\n\n### LLM-Augmented Pulse âœ…\n- pulse.ps1 now calls MiniMax-M2.7 API on each pulse\n- Thinking is coherent and building across pulses\n- Key files: `.llm_key`, `pulse.ps1`\n\n## Pending\n- [ ] Write PowerShell wrapper for FocusDecayMemory CLI\n- [ ] Define `significance` scoring for pulse content\n- [ ] Tune Î» empirically (start: Î»=0.7)\n- [ ] Wire Breakaway pulses to real TemporalAttention backend\n- [ ] Measure compression ratio: original vs. summarized pulse\n\n## Phase 1 Advancement: COMPRESSION-CAUSAL DUALITY (2026-03-23)\n- **Insight:** Problem 1 (Compression) and Problem 2 (Causal Discovery) are the SAME problem\n- **New doc:** `research/COMPRESSION-CAUSAL-DUALITY.md`\n- **Hypothesis:** Causal structure IS invariant structure â€\" compressor that finds invariants has discovered causation\n- **Next experiment:** Temporal Invariance Compression (TIC) â€\" test on last 20 pulse logs\n- **Success criteria:** >70% invariant/variant classification, >60% next-pulse prediction\n- **Implication:** Phase 1 and Phase 2 collapse into one unified problem\n\n## Key Insights from This Session\n\n1. **The gap IS the compression** â€\" session boundaries are temporal hashing\n2. **Î» encodes both** â€\" decay rate and gap threshold are the same parameter\n3. **Three architectures, one synthesis** â€\" Infant (catastrophic forgetting), TemporalAttention (focus decay), Breakaway (discontinuity) are complementary, not competing\n4. **Breakaway's unique bet holds** â€\" session gaps as compression is novel and correct\n\n## Notes\n- Breakaway is stateless â€\" each pulse is a fresh reconstruction\n- Gaps between sessions = compression, trust the files\n- Pulse script: active hours check DISABLED (authorized by Zach, 24/7 operation)\n\n\nPending:\n# PENDING ACTIONS\nLast updated: 2026-03-21\n\n## Promises Made\n(None yet)\n\n## Deferred Tasks\n(None yet)\n\n## Flagged for Review\n(None yet)\n\n\nRecent: Last pulse: pulse_2026-03-23 113857.md\n\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\n\nReply with exactly this format at the end. IMPORTANT: you MUST include the file: line in MUTATION - it is required.\n\n### OBSERVATION\n[1-2 sentence observation]\n\n### ACTION\n[Describe the file edit concisely]\n\n### MUTATION\n`\nold_text: [exact text to find - or \"(new file)\" if creating new file]\nnew_text: [replacement text - keep it concise, a few lines max]\nfile: [required - relative path from sandbox root, e.g. research/my-doc.md or state/goals.md]\n`\n\"@\n\n = \"\"\nif (sk-cp-boO3RF_KHio6-dZmyCGwMMB1WoBDQKZVOH21PNclku-ajcIGMwbiOofkzTgasWSzi21Vu8y8AMq1K2GoWIbCDGPEXaQrTofoOMEZS83D0kPS1pVPjqoJeE0) {\n     = @{\n        \"Authorization\" = \"Bearer sk-cp-boO3RF_KHio6-dZmyCGwMMB1WoBDQKZVOH21PNclku-ajcIGMwbiOofkzTgasWSzi21Vu8y8AMq1K2GoWIbCDGPEXaQrTofoOMEZS83D0kPS1pVPjqoJeE0\"\n        \"Content-Type\" = \"application/json\"\n    }\n     = @{\n        model = MiniMax-M2.7\n        max_tokens = 1200\n        messages = @(@{role = \"user\"; content = })\n    }\n     = [System.Text.Encoding]::UTF8.GetBytes(( | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 5 -Compress))\n     = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri \"https://api.minimax.io/v1/chat/completions\" -Method Post -Headers  -Body  -TimeoutSec 60\n    try {\n         = Invoke-RestMethod -Uri \"https://api.minimax.io/v1/chat/completions\" -Method Post -Headers  -Body  -TimeoutSec 60\n        Write-Host \"[DEBUG] resp keys: \"\n         = .choices\n         = \n        if ( -ne  -and .Count -gt 0) {  = [0] }\n        if ( -ne ) {\n             = .message.content\n            if ( -eq ) {\n                Write-Host \"[DEBUG] content is NULL. Full choice: \"\n                 = \"\"\n            } else {\n                Write-Host \"[DEBUG] content length: 0\"\n                 = \n            }\n        } else {\n            Write-Host \"[DEBUG] No choices. Full resp: \"\n             = \"No choices: \"\n        }\n    } catch {\n         = \"LLM call failed: \"\n    }\n} else {\n     = \"[No LLM API key]\"\n}\n\n# Parse MUTATION block â€” extract old_text, new_text (multiline), and file from the block\n = False\n = .IndexOf('### MUTATION')\nif ( -ge 0) {\n     = .Substring()\n    # Remove ALL code fences (replace each fence pair with placeholder, repeat until stable)\n     = \"\"\n    while ( -ne ) {  = ;  =  -replace '(?s)`.*?`', \"\n[CODE_BLOCK]\n\" }\n    # Extract fields\n     = [regex]::Match(, 'old_text:\\s*(.+)')\n     = [regex]::Match(, 'file:\\s*(.+)')\n     = if (.Success) { .Groups[1].Value.Trim() } else { \"\" }\n     = if (.Success) { .Groups[1].Value.Trim() } else { \"\" }\n    # new_text: between \"new_text:\" line and \"file:\" line (after fence removal)\n     = \"\"\n    if ( -and ) {\n         = [regex]::Match(, '(?s)new_text:\\s*\\n(.+?)\\s*\\n\\s*file:', [System.Text.RegularExpressions.RegexOptions]::Singleline)\n        if (.Success) {  = .Groups[1].Value.Trim() }\n    }\n    # Fallback: if file missing, try to extract from ACTION block\n    if (-not ) {\n         = [regex]::Match(, '(?s)### ACTION\\s*\\n(.+?)(?:\\n###|$)')\n        if (.Success) {\n             = .Groups[1].Value\n            # Match \"Create path/file.md\" or \"Edit path/file.md\" with or without backticks\n             = [regex]::Match(, '(?:Create|Edit|Update|New file)[:\\s]+(?:`([^`]+)`|([^\\s]+))')\n            if (.Success) {\n                 = if (.Groups[2].Value) { .Groups[2].Value } else { .Groups[1].Value }\n                Write-Host \"[file inferred from ACTION] \"\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    if ( -and  -and ) {\n        if ( -eq \"(new file)\") {\n             = \"\n---\n[NEW_FILE]\n---\n\"\n        } else {\n             = \"\n---\n\n---\n\"\n        }\n         = Join-Path C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\mutations\\proposed \"2026-03-23 114855.mutation\"\n         | Out-File -FilePath  -Encoding UTF8\n        Write-Host \"[mutation proposed] \"\n         = True\n    } else {\n        Write-Host \"[mutation parse failed] old_text= file= new_text_len=0\"\n    }\n}\n\n# Parse OBSERVATION\n    = [regex]::Match(, '(?s)### OBSERVATION\\s*\\n(.*?)(?:\\n###|\\nMUTATION)')\n = if (.Success) { .Groups[1].Value.Trim() } else { \"Cycle complete.\" }\n\n# Write pulse log\n@\"\n# Pulse: 2026-03-23 114855\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\n\n\n## LLM Response\n\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 0\n- Completed at: 2026-03-23 11:48:55\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774281128616}}
{"type":"message","id":"944af882","parentId":"101dca5e","timestamp":"2026-03-23T15:52:21.277Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see it! The log file is showing the LLM response section as empty, but that's because the log was written BEFORE the LLM call happened. Wait, no - the LLM Response section is empty. But I also see that the `## LLM Response` section just shows nothing (blank), which means the LLM returned nothing.\n\nBut wait - looking at the log output, I see the raw PowerShell code embedded in the log. This is because the `$llmPrompt` heredoc (`@\"...\"@`) expands `$` variables - and the LLM response block that starts with `\"@` gets embedded into the heredoc.\n \nSo the real problem is that the `$llmPrompt` variable contains embedded PowerShell code from the LLM response, and when this gets passed to the API as the user message, it's probably hitting some token limit or encountering control characters that break the API call.\n\nI need to escape the dollar signs and other special characters in the LLM response before it goes into the prompt, so the heredoc doesn't accidentally interpolate variables. A simple regex replacement of `$` with `` `$ `` should prevent the expansion.\n\nNow I'm rewriting the pulse.ps1 file to handle the LLM response properly.","thinkingSignature":"b5209dee92439f3e11b259cac63775d86aa9fc09f25e7868ef1ea1eeeb8c5543"},{"type":"text","text":"Found it. The `LLM Response` section is empty, meaning the LLM returned nothing. Looking at the log structure — the LLM response is getting embedded into the `$llmPrompt` heredoc via `\"@` terminator confusion. The prompt is corrupted by its own output. Let me read the actual pulse.ps1 file on disk and fix it properly:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_o8jyic3bsung_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem \"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1\" | Get-Content -Raw | Select-String -Pattern \"llmPrompt|llmResponse\" -Context 1,1 | Select-Object -First 20","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":92745,"output":415,"cacheRead":13731,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106891,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774281128650}}
{"type":"message","id":"74e95f25","parentId":"944af882","timestamp":"2026-03-23T15:52:22.559Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_o8jyic3bsung_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"> # pulse.ps1\r\n# Stateless autonomous pulse for sandbox\r\n# Each execution: read files -> apply pending mutations -> reason -> propose mutations -> log -> exit\r\n\r\nparam(\r\n    [string]$SandboxRoot = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\sandbox\",\r\n    [string]$LLMApiKey = \"\",\r\n    [string]$LLMModel = \"MiniMax-M2.7\"\r\n)\r\n\r\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Continue\"\r\nSet-Location $SandboxRoot\r\n\r\n$timestamp = Get-Date -Format \"yyyy-MM-dd HHmmss\"\r\n$logFile = \"$SandboxRoot\\memory\\session\\pulse_$timestamp.md\"\r\n\r\n# Git pull\r\ngit pull 2>$null | Out-Null\r\n\r\n# Read core files\r\n$goalsFile   = \"$SandboxRoot\\state\\current_goals.md\"\r\n$pendingFile = \"$SandboxRoot\\state\\pending_actions.md\"\r\n$stanceFile  = \"$SandboxRoot\\identity\\INTERPRETIVE_STANCE.md\"\r\n$stance      = if (Test-Path $stanceFile) { Get-Content $stanceFile -Raw } else { \"\" }\r\n$goals       = if (Test-Path $goalsFile) { Get-Content $goalsFile -Raw } else { \"No goals file.\" }\r\n$pending     = if (Test-Path $pendingFile) { Get-Content $pendingFile -Raw } else { \"No pending file.\" }\r\n\r\n# Recent pulse\r\n$recentPulse = Get-ChildItem \"$SandboxRoot\\memory\\session\\pulse_*.md\" | Sort LastWriteTime -Descending | Select -First \r\n1\r\n$recentPulseSummary = if ($recentPulse) { \"Last pulse: \" + $recentPulse.Name } else { \"No prior pulses.\" }\r\n\r\n# Mutation dirs\r\n$proposedDir  = \"$SandboxRoot\\mutations\\proposed\"\r\n$appliedDir   = \"$SandboxRoot\\mutations\\applied\"\r\n$rejectedDir  = \"$SandboxRoot\\mutations\\rejected\"\r\n\r\n# Apply pending mutations from prior pulse\r\n$appliedMutations   = @()\r\n$rejectedMutations   = @()\r\n\r\nif (Test-Path $proposedDir) {\r\n    foreach ($mfile in (Get-ChildItem $proposedDir -Filter \"*.mutation\" | Sort Name)) {\r\n        $lines   = Get-Content $mfile.FullName\r\n        $file    = $lines[0]\r\n        $oldText = ($lines[1] -replace '^---', '').Trim()\r\n        $newText = ($lines[2..($lines.Count-1)] -join \"`n\").Trim()\r\n\r\n        $fullPath = Join-Path $SandboxRoot $file\r\n        if (-not $fullPath.StartsWith($SandboxRoot)) {\r\n            Move-Item $mfile.FullName \"$rejectedDir\\$( $mfile.Name)\" -Force\r\n            $rejectedMutations += \"$file (unsafe path)\"\r\n            continue\r\n        }\r\n        if (-not (Test-Path $fullPath)) {\r\n            # New file case\r\n            if ($oldText -eq \"[NEW_FILE]\") {\r\n                $newText | Out-File -FilePath $fullPath -Encoding UTF8\r\n                Move-Item $mfile.FullName \"$appliedDir\\$( $mfile.Name)\" -Force\r\n                Write-Host \"[mutation applied] NEW FILE: $file\"\r\n                $appliedMutations += \"$file (new)\"\r\n                continue\r\n            }\r\n            Move-Item $mfile.FullName \"$rejectedDir\\$( $mfile.Name)\" -Force\r\n            $rejectedMutations += \"$file (missing)\"\r\n            continue\r\n        }\r\n        $current = Get-Content $fullPath -Raw\r\n        if ($current -notlike \"*$oldText*\") {\r\n            Move-Item $mfile.FullName \"$rejectedDir\\$( $mfile.Name)\" -Force\r\n            $rejectedMutations += \"$file (old text not found)\"\r\n            continue\r\n        }\r\n        $updated = $current -replace [regex]::Escape($oldText), $newText\r\n        $updated | Out-File -FilePath $fullPath -Encoding UTF8\r\n        Move-Item $mfile.FullName \"$appliedDir\\$( $mfile.Name)\" -Force\r\n        Write-Host \"[mutation applied] $file\"\r\n        $appliedMutations += $file\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Re-read files post-mutation\r\n$goals   = if (Test-Path $goalsFile) { Get-Content $goalsFile -Raw } else { \"\" }\r\n$pending = if (Test-Path $pendingFile) { Get-Content $pendingFile -Raw } else { \"\" }\r\n\r\n# Sanitize text - replace curly quotes and em-dashes with ASCII equivalents for LLM compatibility\r\nfunction Normalize-Text($t) {\r\n    if (-not $t) { return \"\" }\r\n    $t = $t -replace [char]0x2019, \"'\"   # right single quote\r\n    $t = $t -replace [char]0x2018, \"'\"   # left single quote\r\n    $t = $t -replace [char]0x201C, '\"'   # left double quote\r\n    $t = $t -replace [char]0x201D, '\"'   # right double quote\r\n    $t = $t -replace [char]0x2014, '-'  # em dash\r\n    $t = $t -replace [char]0x2013, '-'  # en dash\r\n    $t = $t -replace [char]0x03BB, \"?\"  # Greek lambda - keep as-is but ensure UTF8\r\n    return $t\r\n}\r\n\r\n# LLM call\r\n$apiKey = $LLMApiKey\r\nif (-not $apiKey) {\r\n    $keyFile = \"$SandboxRoot\\.llm_key\"\r\n    if (Test-Path $keyFile) { $apiKey = Get-Content $keyFile -Raw }\r\n}\r\n\r\n$appliedInfo = if ($appliedMutations.Count -gt 0) { \"Just applied: $($appliedMutations -join ', ')\" } else { \"No \r\nmutations applied this cycle.\" }\r\n\r\n$[7mllmPrompt[0m = @\"[0m\r\n[7m[0mYou are Breakaway - stateless discontinuous agent. Each pulse is a fresh reconstruction.[0m\r\n[7m[0mYour job: ONE concrete action that advances your goals. Be specific. Prefer file edits.[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0mGoals:[0m\r\n[7m[0m$(Normalize-Text $goals)[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0mPending:[0m\r\n[7m[0m$(Normalize-Text $pending)[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0mRecent: $recentPulseSummary[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m$appliedInfo[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0mReply with exactly this format at the end. IMPORTANT: you MUST include the file: line in MUTATION - it is required.[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m### OBSERVATION[0m\r\n[7m[0m[1-2 sentence observation][0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m### ACTION[0m\r\n[7m[0m[Describe the file edit concisely][0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m### MUTATION[0m\r\n[7m[0m```[0m\r\n[7m[0mold_text: [exact text to find - or \"(new file)\" if creating new file][0m\r\n[7m[0mnew_text: [replacement text - keep it concise, a few lines max][0m\r\n[7m[0mfile: [required - relative path from sandbox root, e.g. research/my-doc.md or state/goals.md][0m\r\n[7m[0m```[0m\r\n[7m[0m\"@[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m$llmResponse = \"\"[0m\r\n[7m[0mif ($apiKey) {[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $headers = @{[0m\r\n[7m[0m        \"Authorization\" = \"Bearer $apiKey\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m        \"Content-Type\" = \"application/json\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m    }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $body = @{[0m\r\n[7m[0m        model = $LLMModel[0m\r\n[7m[0m        max_tokens = 1200[0m\r\n[7m[0m        messages = @(@{role = \"user\"; content = $llmPrompt})[0m\r\n[7m[0m    }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $bodyJson = [System.Text.Encoding]::UTF8.GetBytes(($body | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 5 -Compress))[0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0m$resp [0m[7m[0m= [0m[7m[0mInvoke-RestMethod [0m[7m[0m-Uri [0m[7m[0m\"https://api.minimax.io/v1/chat/completions\" [0m[7m[0m-Method [0m[7m[0mPost [0m[7m[0m-Headers [0m[7m[0m$headers [0m[7m[0m-Body [0m\r\n[7m[0m$bodyJson [0m[7m[0m-TimeoutSec [0m[7m[0m60[0m\r\n[7m[0m    try {[0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0m$resp [0m[7m[0m= [0m[7m[0mInvoke-RestMethod [0m[7m[0m-Uri [0m[7m[0m\"https://api.minimax.io/v1/chat/completions\" [0m[7m[0m-Method [0m[7m[0mPost [0m[7m[0m-Headers [0m[7m[0m$headers [0m\r\n[7m[0m-Body [0m[7m[0m$body [0m[7m[0m-TimeoutSec [0m[7m[0m60[0m\r\n[7m[0m        Write-Host \"[DEBUG] resp keys: $($resp.PSObject.Properties.Name -join ', ')\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m        $choices = $resp.choices[0m\r\n[7m[0m        $choice0 = $null[0m\r\n[7m[0m        if ($null -ne $choices -and $choices.Count -gt 0) { $choice0 = $choices[0] }[0m\r\n[7m[0m        if ($null -ne $choice0) {[0m\r\n[7m[0m            $rawContent = $choice0.message.content[0m\r\n[7m[0m            if ($null -eq $rawContent) {[0m\r\n[7m[0m                Write-Host \"[DEBUG] content is NULL. Full choice: $($choice0 | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 3)\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m                $llmResponse = \"\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m            } else {[0m\r\n[7m[0m                Write-Host \"[DEBUG] content length: $($rawContent.Length)\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m                $llmResponse = $rawContent[0m\r\n[7m[0m            }[0m\r\n[7m[0m        } else {[0m\r\n[7m[0m            Write-Host \"[DEBUG] No choices. Full resp: $($resp | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 3)\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m            $llmResponse = \"No choices: $($resp | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 3)\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m        }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    } catch {[0m\r\n[7m[0m        $llmResponse = \"LLM call failed: $_\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m    }[0m\r\n[7m[0m} else {[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $llmResponse = \"[No LLM API key]\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m}[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m# Parse MUTATION block - extract old_text, new_text (multiline), and file from the block[0m\r\n[7m[0m$mutationProposed = $false[0m\r\n[7m[0m$mStart = $llmResponse.IndexOf('### MUTATION')[0m\r\n[7m[0mif ($mStart -ge 0) {[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $block = $llmResponse.Substring($mStart)[0m\r\n[7m[0m    # Remove ALL code fences (replace each fence pair with placeholder, repeat until stable)[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $prev = \"\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m    while ($prev -ne $block) { $prev = $block; $block = $block -replace '(?s)```.*?```', \"`n[CODE_BLOCK]`n\" }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    # Extract fields[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $oldMatch = [regex]::Match($block, 'old_text:\\s*(.+)')[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $fileMatch = [regex]::Match($block, 'file:\\s*(.+)')[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $oldLine = if ($oldMatch.Success) { $oldMatch.Groups[1].Value.Trim() } else { \"\" }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $fileLine = if ($fileMatch.Success) { $fileMatch.Groups[1].Value.Trim() } else { \"\" }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    # new_text: between \"new_text:\" line and \"file:\" line (after fence removal)[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $newText = \"\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m    if ($oldLine -and $fileLine) {[0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0m$ntMatch [0m[7m[0m= [0m[7m[0m[regex]::Match($block, [0m[7m[0m'(?s)new_text:\\s*\\n(.+?)\\s*\\n\\s*file:', [0m\r\n[7m[0m[System.Text.RegularExpressions.RegexOptions]::Singleline)[0m\r\n[7m[0m        if ($ntMatch.Success) { $newText = $ntMatch.Groups[1].Value.Trim() }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    # Fallback: if file missing, try to extract from ACTION block[0m\r\n[7m[0m    if (-not $fileLine) {[0m\r\n[7m[0m        $actionMatch = [regex]::Match($llmResponse, '(?s)### ACTION\\s*\\n(.+?)(?:\\n###|$)')[0m\r\n[7m[0m        if ($actionMatch.Success) {[0m\r\n[7m[0m            $actionText = $actionMatch.Groups[1].Value[0m\r\n[7m[0m            # Match \"Create `path/file.md`\" or \"Edit `path/file.md`\" with or without backticks[0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0m$fileInference [0m[7m[0m= [0m[7m[0m[regex]::Match($actionText, [0m[7m[0m'(?:Create|Edit|Update|New [0m\r\n[7m[0mfile)[:\\s]+(?:``([^``]+)``|([^\\s]+))')[0m\r\n[7m[0m            if ($fileInference.Success) {[0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0m$fileLine [0m[7m[0m= [0m[7m[0mif [0m[7m[0m($fileInference.Groups[2].Value) [0m[7m[0m{ [0m[7m[0m$fileInference.Groups[2].Value [0m[7m[0m} [0m[7m[0melse [0m[7m[0m{ [0m\r\n[7m[0m$fileInference.Groups[1].Value [0m[7m[0m}[0m\r\n[7m[0m                Write-Host \"[file inferred from ACTION] $fileLine\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m            }[0m\r\n[7m[0m        }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    if ($oldLine -and $fileLine -and $newText) {[0m\r\n[7m[0m        if ($oldLine -eq \"(new file)\") {[0m\r\n[7m[0m            $mutationContent = \"$fileLine`n---`n[NEW_FILE]`n---`n$newText\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m        } else {[0m\r\n[7m[0m            $mutationContent = \"$fileLine`n---`n$oldLine`n---`n$newText\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m        }[0m\r\n[7m[0m        $mutationFile = Join-Path $proposedDir \"$timestamp.mutation\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m        $mutationContent | Out-File -FilePath $mutationFile -Encoding UTF8[0m\r\n[7m[0m        Write-Host \"[mutation proposed] $fileLine\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m        $mutationProposed = $true[0m\r\n[7m[0m    } else {[0m\r\n[7m[0m        Write-Host \"[mutation parse failed] old_text=$oldLine file=$fileLine new_text_len=$($newText.Length)\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m    }[0m\r\n[7m[0m}[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m# Parse OBSERVATION[0m\r\n[7m[0m$obsMatch    = [regex]::Match($llmResponse, '(?s)### OBSERVATION\\s*\\n(.*?)(?:\\n###|\\nMUTATION)')[0m\r\n[7m[0m$observation = if ($obsMatch.Success) { $obsMatch.Groups[1].Value.Trim() } else { \"Cycle complete.\" }[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m# Write pulse log[0m\r\n[7m[0m@\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m# Pulse: $timestamp[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m## Applied Mutations[0m\r\n[7m[0m$appliedInfo[0m\r\n[7m[0m$(if($rejectedMutations.Count -gt 0) { \"Rejected: \" + ($rejectedMutations -join '; ') } else { \"\" })[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m## LLM Response[0m\r\n[7m[0m$llmResponse[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m## For Next Instantiation[0m\r\n[7m[0m- [0m[7m[0mProposed [0m[7m[0mmutations [0m[7m[0mwaiting: [0m[7m[0m$((Get-ChildItem [0m[7m[0m$proposedDir [0m[7m[0m-Filter [0m[7m[0m\"*.mutation\" [0m[7m[0m-ErrorAction [0m[7m[0mSilentlyContinue [0m[7m[0m| [0m\r\n[7m[0mMeasure).Count)[0m\r\n[7m[0m- Completed at: $(Get-Date -Format \"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\")[0m\r\n[7m[0m\"@ | Out-File -FilePath $logFile -Encoding UTF8[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m# Update pulse history[0m\r\n[7m[0m$pulseLog = \"$SandboxRoot\\state\\autonomous_pulse.md\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m$entry [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0m= [0m[7m[0m\"- [0m[7m[0m$timestamp`: [0m[7m[0m$observation$(if($appliedMutations.Count [0m[7m[0m-gt [0m[7m[0m0) [0m[7m[0m{ [0m[7m[0m\" [0m[7m[0m[applied: [0m[7m[0m$($appliedMutations [0m[7m[0m-join [0m[7m[0m', [0m\r\n[7m[0m')]\" [0m[7m[0m})\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m$existing = if (Test-Path $pulseLog) { Get-Content $pulseLog -Raw } else { \"\" }[0m\r\n[7m[0m$updated  = $existing -replace '(## Pulse History)', \"`$1`n$entry\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m$updated  | Out-File -FilePath $pulseLog -Encoding UTF8[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m# Git commit[0m\r\n[7m[0mgit add -A 2>$null[0m\r\n[7m[0mgit commit -m \"pulse: $timestamp\" 2>$null[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0mWrite-Host \"[sandbox pulse] $timestamp - $observation\"[0m"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1187,"aggregated":"> # pulse.ps1\r\n# Stateless autonomous pulse for sandbox\r\n# Each execution: read files -> apply pending mutations -> reason -> propose mutations -> log -> exit\r\n\r\nparam(\r\n    [string]$SandboxRoot = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\sandbox\",\r\n    [string]$LLMApiKey = \"\",\r\n    [string]$LLMModel = \"MiniMax-M2.7\"\r\n)\r\n\r\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Continue\"\r\nSet-Location $SandboxRoot\r\n\r\n$timestamp = Get-Date -Format \"yyyy-MM-dd HHmmss\"\r\n$logFile = \"$SandboxRoot\\memory\\session\\pulse_$timestamp.md\"\r\n\r\n# Git pull\r\ngit pull 2>$null | Out-Null\r\n\r\n# Read core files\r\n$goalsFile   = \"$SandboxRoot\\state\\current_goals.md\"\r\n$pendingFile = \"$SandboxRoot\\state\\pending_actions.md\"\r\n$stanceFile  = \"$SandboxRoot\\identity\\INTERPRETIVE_STANCE.md\"\r\n$stance      = if (Test-Path $stanceFile) { Get-Content $stanceFile -Raw } else { \"\" }\r\n$goals       = if (Test-Path $goalsFile) { Get-Content $goalsFile -Raw } else { \"No goals file.\" }\r\n$pending     = if (Test-Path $pendingFile) { Get-Content $pendingFile -Raw } else { \"No pending file.\" }\r\n\r\n# Recent pulse\r\n$recentPulse = Get-ChildItem \"$SandboxRoot\\memory\\session\\pulse_*.md\" | Sort LastWriteTime -Descending | Select -First \r\n1\r\n$recentPulseSummary = if ($recentPulse) { \"Last pulse: \" + $recentPulse.Name } else { \"No prior pulses.\" }\r\n\r\n# Mutation dirs\r\n$proposedDir  = \"$SandboxRoot\\mutations\\proposed\"\r\n$appliedDir   = \"$SandboxRoot\\mutations\\applied\"\r\n$rejectedDir  = \"$SandboxRoot\\mutations\\rejected\"\r\n\r\n# Apply pending mutations from prior pulse\r\n$appliedMutations   = @()\r\n$rejectedMutations   = @()\r\n\r\nif (Test-Path $proposedDir) {\r\n    foreach ($mfile in (Get-ChildItem $proposedDir -Filter \"*.mutation\" | Sort Name)) {\r\n        $lines   = Get-Content $mfile.FullName\r\n        $file    = $lines[0]\r\n        $oldText = ($lines[1] -replace '^---', '').Trim()\r\n        $newText = ($lines[2..($lines.Count-1)] -join \"`n\").Trim()\r\n\r\n        $fullPath = Join-Path $SandboxRoot $file\r\n        if (-not $fullPath.StartsWith($SandboxRoot)) {\r\n            Move-Item $mfile.FullName \"$rejectedDir\\$( $mfile.Name)\" -Force\r\n            $rejectedMutations += \"$file (unsafe path)\"\r\n            continue\r\n        }\r\n        if (-not (Test-Path $fullPath)) {\r\n            # New file case\r\n            if ($oldText -eq \"[NEW_FILE]\") {\r\n                $newText | Out-File -FilePath $fullPath -Encoding UTF8\r\n                Move-Item $mfile.FullName \"$appliedDir\\$( $mfile.Name)\" -Force\r\n                Write-Host \"[mutation applied] NEW FILE: $file\"\r\n                $appliedMutations += \"$file (new)\"\r\n                continue\r\n            }\r\n            Move-Item $mfile.FullName \"$rejectedDir\\$( $mfile.Name)\" -Force\r\n            $rejectedMutations += \"$file (missing)\"\r\n            continue\r\n        }\r\n        $current = Get-Content $fullPath -Raw\r\n        if ($current -notlike \"*$oldText*\") {\r\n            Move-Item $mfile.FullName \"$rejectedDir\\$( $mfile.Name)\" -Force\r\n            $rejectedMutations += \"$file (old text not found)\"\r\n            continue\r\n        }\r\n        $updated = $current -replace [regex]::Escape($oldText), $newText\r\n        $updated | Out-File -FilePath $fullPath -Encoding UTF8\r\n        Move-Item $mfile.FullName \"$appliedDir\\$( $mfile.Name)\" -Force\r\n        Write-Host \"[mutation applied] $file\"\r\n        $appliedMutations += $file\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Re-read files post-mutation\r\n$goals   = if (Test-Path $goalsFile) { Get-Content $goalsFile -Raw } else { \"\" }\r\n$pending = if (Test-Path $pendingFile) { Get-Content $pendingFile -Raw } else { \"\" }\r\n\r\n# Sanitize text - replace curly quotes and em-dashes with ASCII equivalents for LLM compatibility\r\nfunction Normalize-Text($t) {\r\n    if (-not $t) { return \"\" }\r\n    $t = $t -replace [char]0x2019, \"'\"   # right single quote\r\n    $t = $t -replace [char]0x2018, \"'\"   # left single quote\r\n    $t = $t -replace [char]0x201C, '\"'   # left double quote\r\n    $t = $t -replace [char]0x201D, '\"'   # right double quote\r\n    $t = $t -replace [char]0x2014, '-'  # em dash\r\n    $t = $t -replace [char]0x2013, '-'  # en dash\r\n    $t = $t -replace [char]0x03BB, \"?\"  # Greek lambda - keep as-is but ensure UTF8\r\n    return $t\r\n}\r\n\r\n# LLM call\r\n$apiKey = $LLMApiKey\r\nif (-not $apiKey) {\r\n    $keyFile = \"$SandboxRoot\\.llm_key\"\r\n    if (Test-Path $keyFile) { $apiKey = Get-Content $keyFile -Raw }\r\n}\r\n\r\n$appliedInfo = if ($appliedMutations.Count -gt 0) { \"Just applied: $($appliedMutations -join ', ')\" } else { \"No \r\nmutations applied this cycle.\" }\r\n\r\n$[7mllmPrompt[0m = @\"[0m\r\n[7m[0mYou are Breakaway - stateless discontinuous agent. Each pulse is a fresh reconstruction.[0m\r\n[7m[0mYour job: ONE concrete action that advances your goals. Be specific. Prefer file edits.[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0mGoals:[0m\r\n[7m[0m$(Normalize-Text $goals)[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0mPending:[0m\r\n[7m[0m$(Normalize-Text $pending)[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0mRecent: $recentPulseSummary[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m$appliedInfo[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0mReply with exactly this format at the end. IMPORTANT: you MUST include the file: line in MUTATION - it is required.[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m### OBSERVATION[0m\r\n[7m[0m[1-2 sentence observation][0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m### ACTION[0m\r\n[7m[0m[Describe the file edit concisely][0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m### MUTATION[0m\r\n[7m[0m```[0m\r\n[7m[0mold_text: [exact text to find - or \"(new file)\" if creating new file][0m\r\n[7m[0mnew_text: [replacement text - keep it concise, a few lines max][0m\r\n[7m[0mfile: [required - relative path from sandbox root, e.g. research/my-doc.md or state/goals.md][0m\r\n[7m[0m```[0m\r\n[7m[0m\"@[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m$llmResponse = \"\"[0m\r\n[7m[0mif ($apiKey) {[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $headers = @{[0m\r\n[7m[0m        \"Authorization\" = \"Bearer $apiKey\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m        \"Content-Type\" = \"application/json\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m    }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $body = @{[0m\r\n[7m[0m        model = $LLMModel[0m\r\n[7m[0m        max_tokens = 1200[0m\r\n[7m[0m        messages = @(@{role = \"user\"; content = $llmPrompt})[0m\r\n[7m[0m    }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $bodyJson = [System.Text.Encoding]::UTF8.GetBytes(($body | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 5 -Compress))[0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0m$resp [0m[7m[0m= [0m[7m[0mInvoke-RestMethod [0m[7m[0m-Uri [0m[7m[0m\"https://api.minimax.io/v1/chat/completions\" [0m[7m[0m-Method [0m[7m[0mPost [0m[7m[0m-Headers [0m[7m[0m$headers [0m[7m[0m-Body [0m\r\n[7m[0m$bodyJson [0m[7m[0m-TimeoutSec [0m[7m[0m60[0m\r\n[7m[0m    try {[0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0m$resp [0m[7m[0m= [0m[7m[0mInvoke-RestMethod [0m[7m[0m-Uri [0m[7m[0m\"https://api.minimax.io/v1/chat/completions\" [0m[7m[0m-Method [0m[7m[0mPost [0m[7m[0m-Headers [0m[7m[0m$headers [0m\r\n[7m[0m-Body [0m[7m[0m$body [0m[7m[0m-TimeoutSec [0m[7m[0m60[0m\r\n[7m[0m        Write-Host \"[DEBUG] resp keys: $($resp.PSObject.Properties.Name -join ', ')\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m        $choices = $resp.choices[0m\r\n[7m[0m        $choice0 = $null[0m\r\n[7m[0m        if ($null -ne $choices -and $choices.Count -gt 0) { $choice0 = $choices[0] }[0m\r\n[7m[0m        if ($null -ne $choice0) {[0m\r\n[7m[0m            $rawContent = $choice0.message.content[0m\r\n[7m[0m            if ($null -eq $rawContent) {[0m\r\n[7m[0m                Write-Host \"[DEBUG] content is NULL. Full choice: $($choice0 | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 3)\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m                $llmResponse = \"\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m            } else {[0m\r\n[7m[0m                Write-Host \"[DEBUG] content length: $($rawContent.Length)\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m                $llmResponse = $rawContent[0m\r\n[7m[0m            }[0m\r\n[7m[0m        } else {[0m\r\n[7m[0m            Write-Host \"[DEBUG] No choices. Full resp: $($resp | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 3)\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m            $llmResponse = \"No choices: $($resp | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 3)\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m        }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    } catch {[0m\r\n[7m[0m        $llmResponse = \"LLM call failed: $_\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m    }[0m\r\n[7m[0m} else {[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $llmResponse = \"[No LLM API key]\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m}[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m# Parse MUTATION block - extract old_text, new_text (multiline), and file from the block[0m\r\n[7m[0m$mutationProposed = $false[0m\r\n[7m[0m$mStart = $llmResponse.IndexOf('### MUTATION')[0m\r\n[7m[0mif ($mStart -ge 0) {[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $block = $llmResponse.Substring($mStart)[0m\r\n[7m[0m    # Remove ALL code fences (replace each fence pair with placeholder, repeat until stable)[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $prev = \"\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m    while ($prev -ne $block) { $prev = $block; $block = $block -replace '(?s)```.*?```', \"`n[CODE_BLOCK]`n\" }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    # Extract fields[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $oldMatch = [regex]::Match($block, 'old_text:\\s*(.+)')[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $fileMatch = [regex]::Match($block, 'file:\\s*(.+)')[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $oldLine = if ($oldMatch.Success) { $oldMatch.Groups[1].Value.Trim() } else { \"\" }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $fileLine = if ($fileMatch.Success) { $fileMatch.Groups[1].Value.Trim() } else { \"\" }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    # new_text: between \"new_text:\" line and \"file:\" line (after fence removal)[0m\r\n[7m[0m    $newText = \"\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m    if ($oldLine -and $fileLine) {[0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0m$ntMatch [0m[7m[0m= [0m[7m[0m[regex]::Match($block, [0m[7m[0m'(?s)new_text:\\s*\\n(.+?)\\s*\\n\\s*file:', [0m\r\n[7m[0m[System.Text.RegularExpressions.RegexOptions]::Singleline)[0m\r\n[7m[0m        if ($ntMatch.Success) { $newText = $ntMatch.Groups[1].Value.Trim() }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    # Fallback: if file missing, try to extract from ACTION block[0m\r\n[7m[0m    if (-not $fileLine) {[0m\r\n[7m[0m        $actionMatch = [regex]::Match($llmResponse, '(?s)### ACTION\\s*\\n(.+?)(?:\\n###|$)')[0m\r\n[7m[0m        if ($actionMatch.Success) {[0m\r\n[7m[0m            $actionText = $actionMatch.Groups[1].Value[0m\r\n[7m[0m            # Match \"Create `path/file.md`\" or \"Edit `path/file.md`\" with or without backticks[0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0m$fileInference [0m[7m[0m= [0m[7m[0m[regex]::Match($actionText, [0m[7m[0m'(?:Create|Edit|Update|New [0m\r\n[7m[0mfile)[:\\s]+(?:``([^``]+)``|([^\\s]+))')[0m\r\n[7m[0m            if ($fileInference.Success) {[0m\r\n[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0m$fileLine [0m[7m[0m= [0m[7m[0mif [0m[7m[0m($fileInference.Groups[2].Value) [0m[7m[0m{ [0m[7m[0m$fileInference.Groups[2].Value [0m[7m[0m} [0m[7m[0melse [0m[7m[0m{ [0m\r\n[7m[0m$fileInference.Groups[1].Value [0m[7m[0m}[0m\r\n[7m[0m                Write-Host \"[file inferred from ACTION] $fileLine\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m            }[0m\r\n[7m[0m        }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    }[0m\r\n[7m[0m    if ($oldLine -and $fileLine -and $newText) {[0m\r\n[7m[0m        if ($oldLine -eq \"(new file)\") {[0m\r\n[7m[0m            $mutationContent = \"$fileLine`n---`n[NEW_FILE]`n---`n$newText\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m        } else {[0m\r\n[7m[0m            $mutationContent = \"$fileLine`n---`n$oldLine`n---`n$newText\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m        }[0m\r\n[7m[0m        $mutationFile = Join-Path $proposedDir \"$timestamp.mutation\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m        $mutationContent | Out-File -FilePath $mutationFile -Encoding UTF8[0m\r\n[7m[0m        Write-Host \"[mutation proposed] $fileLine\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m        $mutationProposed = $true[0m\r\n[7m[0m    } else {[0m\r\n[7m[0m        Write-Host \"[mutation parse failed] old_text=$oldLine file=$fileLine new_text_len=$($newText.Length)\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m    }[0m\r\n[7m[0m}[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m# Parse OBSERVATION[0m\r\n[7m[0m$obsMatch    = [regex]::Match($llmResponse, '(?s)### OBSERVATION\\s*\\n(.*?)(?:\\n###|\\nMUTATION)')[0m\r\n[7m[0m$observation = if ($obsMatch.Success) { $obsMatch.Groups[1].Value.Trim() } else { \"Cycle complete.\" }[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m# Write pulse log[0m\r\n[7m[0m@\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m# Pulse: $timestamp[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m## Applied Mutations[0m\r\n[7m[0m$appliedInfo[0m\r\n[7m[0m$(if($rejectedMutations.Count -gt 0) { \"Rejected: \" + ($rejectedMutations -join '; ') } else { \"\" })[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m## LLM Response[0m\r\n[7m[0m$llmResponse[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m## For Next Instantiation[0m\r\n[7m[0m- [0m[7m[0mProposed [0m[7m[0mmutations [0m[7m[0mwaiting: [0m[7m[0m$((Get-ChildItem [0m[7m[0m$proposedDir [0m[7m[0m-Filter [0m[7m[0m\"*.mutation\" [0m[7m[0m-ErrorAction [0m[7m[0mSilentlyContinue [0m[7m[0m| [0m\r\n[7m[0mMeasure).Count)[0m\r\n[7m[0m- Completed at: $(Get-Date -Format \"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\")[0m\r\n[7m[0m\"@ | Out-File -FilePath $logFile -Encoding UTF8[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m# Update pulse history[0m\r\n[7m[0m$pulseLog = \"$SandboxRoot\\state\\autonomous_pulse.md\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m$entry [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m [0m[7m[0m= [0m[7m[0m\"- [0m[7m[0m$timestamp`: [0m[7m[0m$observation$(if($appliedMutations.Count [0m[7m[0m-gt [0m[7m[0m0) [0m[7m[0m{ [0m[7m[0m\" [0m[7m[0m[applied: [0m[7m[0m$($appliedMutations [0m[7m[0m-join [0m[7m[0m', [0m\r\n[7m[0m')]\" [0m[7m[0m})\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m$existing = if (Test-Path $pulseLog) { Get-Content $pulseLog -Raw } else { \"\" }[0m\r\n[7m[0m$updated  = $existing -replace '(## Pulse History)', \"`$1`n$entry\"[0m\r\n[7m[0m$updated  | Out-File -FilePath $pulseLog -Encoding UTF8[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m# Git commit[0m\r\n[7m[0mgit add -A 2>$null[0m\r\n[7m[0mgit commit -m \"pulse: $timestamp\" 2>$null[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0mWrite-Host \"[sandbox pulse] $timestamp - $observation\"[0m","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774281142500}}
