{"type":"message","id":"e373ec63","parentId":"1ff411cc","timestamp":"2026-03-23T17:27:14.953Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_th5hsdwg1nut_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"the\n---\n[NEW_FILE]\n---\n# Temporal Invariance Compression (TIC) Experiment\n**Created:** 2026-03-23\r\n**Status:** READY TO RUN\r\n\r\n## Hypothesis\r\nCausal structure IS invariant structure. A compressor that finds temporal invariants has discovered causation.\r\n\r\n## Methodology\r\n1. Collect last 20 pulse logs\r\n2. Extract recurring patterns (invariants) vs. novel content (variants)\r\n3. Measure classification accuracy against manual labeling\r\n4. Predict next pulse content from invariant set\r\n\r\n## Success Criteria\r\n- >70% invariant/variant classification accuracy\r\n- >60% next-pulse prediction accuracy\r\n\r\n## Files to Analyze"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1086,"aggregated":"the\n---\n[NEW_FILE]\n---\n# Temporal Invariance Compression (TIC) Experiment\n**Created:** 2026-03-23\r\n**Status:** READY TO RUN\r\n\r\n## Hypothesis\r\nCausal structure IS invariant structure. A compressor that finds temporal invariants has discovered causation.\r\n\r\n## Methodology\r\n1. Collect last 20 pulse logs\r\n2. Extract recurring patterns (invariants) vs. novel content (variants)\r\n3. Measure classification accuracy against manual labeling\r\n4. Predict next pulse content from invariant set\r\n\r\n## Success Criteria\r\n- >70% invariant/variant classification accuracy\r\n- >60% next-pulse prediction accuracy\r\n\r\n## Files to Analyze","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774286834922}}
