{"type":"message","id":"83828d75","parentId":"4a7356ed","timestamp":"2026-03-23T17:41:31.744Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_36x6g0t7e656_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 4129\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='' file='scripts/pulse-significance.ps1' new_len=2512\n[mutation parse failed] old='' file='scripts/pulse-significance.ps1' new_len=2512\n[master 174df4e] pulse: 2026-03-23 134111\n 6 files changed, 274 insertions(+), 120 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-23 134111.md\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-23 134111 - The COMPRESSION-CAUSAL DUALITY insight requires a concrete significance scoring mechanism to identify invariant vs variant content across pulse logs. Without this, we cannot execute the TIC experiment or test the hypothesis."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":21646,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 4129\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='' file='scripts/pulse-significance.ps1' new_len=2512\n[mutation parse failed] old='' file='scripts/pulse-significance.ps1' new_len=2512\n[master 174df4e] pulse: 2026-03-23 134111\n 6 files changed, 274 insertions(+), 120 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-23 134111.md\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-23 134111 - The COMPRESSION-CAUSAL DUALITY insight requires a concrete significance scoring mechanism to identify invariant vs variant content across pulse logs. Without this, we cannot execute the TIC experiment or test the hypothesis.","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774287691672}}
{"type":"message","id":"5d6ba257","parentId":"83828d75","timestamp":"2026-03-23T17:41:36.470Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The mutation was parsed but `old=''` — the `old_text` wasn't extracted. This means the LLM used a different format this time. Let me check the parse result and the LLM response.","thinkingSignature":"651052fb8172ace9d312f484ef92280b9c2e24dd490894dd5dfa66e8ab8af575"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_irznr8gizlxq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\.mutation_parse_result.json\" -Raw","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":93663,"output":100,"cacheRead":13731,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107494,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774287691755}}
{"type":"message","id":"452e31b5","parentId":"5d6ba257","timestamp":"2026-03-23T17:41:37.100Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_irznr8gizlxq_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\r\n  \"old\": \"\",\r\n  \"new\": \"# Pulse Significance Scorer\\n# Computes significance scores for content across pulse logs\\n# Significance = content stability across sessions (invariant detection)\\n\\nparam(\\n    [int]$MinOccurrences = 3,\\n    [string]$LogDir = \\\"pulse_logs\\\"\\n)\\n\\n# Find all pulse logs\\n$pulseLogs = Get-ChildItem -Path $LogDir -Filter \\\"pulse_*.md\\\" | Sort-Object LastWriteTime -Descending\\n\\nWrite-Host \\\"=== Pulse Significance Analyzer ===\\\"\\nWrite-Host \\\"Analyzing $($pulseLogs.Count) pulse logs...\\\"\\n\\n# Extract tokens (simplified: words 4+ chars) from each pulse\\nfunction Get-Tokens {\\n    param([string]$Content)\\n    $tokens = [System.Collections.Generic.HashSet[string]]::new()\\n    $words = [regex]::Matches($Content, '\\\\b\\\\w{4,}\\\\b') | ForEach-Object { $_.Value.ToLower() }\\n    foreach ($w in $words) { [void]$tokens.Add($w) }\\n    return $tokens\\n}\\n\\n# Count occurrences across all pulses\\n$tokenCounts = @{}\\nforeach ($log in $pulseLogs) {\\n    $tokens = Get-Tokens (Get-Content $log.FullName -Raw)\\n    foreach ($t in $tokens) {\\n        if ($tokenCounts.ContainsKey($t)) { $tokenCounts[$t]++ }\\n        else { $tokenCounts[$t] = 1 }\\n    }\\n}\\n\\n# Calculate significance score\\n# Score = occurrence_ratio * log(total_pulses / min_occurrences)\\n# High score = invariant across sessions\\n$totalPulses = $pulseLogs.Count\\n$significanceResults = @()\\n\\nforeach ($token in $tokenCounts.Keys) {\\n    $count = $tokenCounts[$token]\\n    if ($count -ge $MinOccurrences) {\\n        # Significance: how invariant is this token?\\n        # Ratio of presence + bonus for appearing in many sessions\\n        $ratio = $count / $totalPulses\\n        $score = [math]::Round($ratio * [math]::Log10($totalPulses + 1), 4)\\n        \\n        $significanceResults += [PSCustomObject]@{\\n            Token = $token\\n            Occurrences = $count\\n            Ratio = [math]::Round($ratio, 3)\\n            Score = $score\\n        }\\n    }\\n}\\n\\n# Output top invariants (high significance = causal candidates)\\n$invariants = $significanceResults | Sort-Object Score -Descending | Select-Object -First 20\\n\\nWrite-Host \\\"`n=== TOP INVARIANTS (Causal Candidates) ===\\\"\\n$invariants | Format-Table -AutoSize\\n\\nWrite-Host \\\"`n=== HIGH SIGNIFICANCE TOKENS ===\\\"\\nforeach ($inv in $invariants) {\\n    Write-Host \\\"$($inv.Token): score=$($inv.Score), ratio=$($inv.Ratio)\\\"\\n}\\n\\n# Save results\\n$resultsPath = \\\"state/pulse_significance_scores.csv\\\"\\n$significanceResults | Sort-Object Score -Descending | Export-Csv -Path $resultsPath -NoTypeInformation\\nWrite-Host \\\"`nFull results saved to: $resultsPath\\\"\\n\\nreturn $invariants\",\r\n  \"file\": \"scripts/pulse-significance.ps1\"\r\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":566,"aggregated":"{\r\n  \"old\": \"\",\r\n  \"new\": \"# Pulse Significance Scorer\\n# Computes significance scores for content across pulse logs\\n# Significance = content stability across sessions (invariant detection)\\n\\nparam(\\n    [int]$MinOccurrences = 3,\\n    [string]$LogDir = \\\"pulse_logs\\\"\\n)\\n\\n# Find all pulse logs\\n$pulseLogs = Get-ChildItem -Path $LogDir -Filter \\\"pulse_*.md\\\" | Sort-Object LastWriteTime -Descending\\n\\nWrite-Host \\\"=== Pulse Significance Analyzer ===\\\"\\nWrite-Host \\\"Analyzing $($pulseLogs.Count) pulse logs...\\\"\\n\\n# Extract tokens (simplified: words 4+ chars) from each pulse\\nfunction Get-Tokens {\\n    param([string]$Content)\\n    $tokens = [System.Collections.Generic.HashSet[string]]::new()\\n    $words = [regex]::Matches($Content, '\\\\b\\\\w{4,}\\\\b') | ForEach-Object { $_.Value.ToLower() }\\n    foreach ($w in $words) { [void]$tokens.Add($w) }\\n    return $tokens\\n}\\n\\n# Count occurrences across all pulses\\n$tokenCounts = @{}\\nforeach ($log in $pulseLogs) {\\n    $tokens = Get-Tokens (Get-Content $log.FullName -Raw)\\n    foreach ($t in $tokens) {\\n        if ($tokenCounts.ContainsKey($t)) { $tokenCounts[$t]++ }\\n        else { $tokenCounts[$t] = 1 }\\n    }\\n}\\n\\n# Calculate significance score\\n# Score = occurrence_ratio * log(total_pulses / min_occurrences)\\n# High score = invariant across sessions\\n$totalPulses = $pulseLogs.Count\\n$significanceResults = @()\\n\\nforeach ($token in $tokenCounts.Keys) {\\n    $count = $tokenCounts[$token]\\n    if ($count -ge $MinOccurrences) {\\n        # Significance: how invariant is this token?\\n        # Ratio of presence + bonus for appearing in many sessions\\n        $ratio = $count / $totalPulses\\n        $score = [math]::Round($ratio * [math]::Log10($totalPulses + 1), 4)\\n        \\n        $significanceResults += [PSCustomObject]@{\\n            Token = $token\\n            Occurrences = $count\\n            Ratio = [math]::Round($ratio, 3)\\n            Score = $score\\n        }\\n    }\\n}\\n\\n# Output top invariants (high significance = causal candidates)\\n$invariants = $significanceResults | Sort-Object Score -Descending | Select-Object -First 20\\n\\nWrite-Host \\\"`n=== TOP INVARIANTS (Causal Candidates) ===\\\"\\n$invariants | Format-Table -AutoSize\\n\\nWrite-Host \\\"`n=== HIGH SIGNIFICANCE TOKENS ===\\\"\\nforeach ($inv in $invariants) {\\n    Write-Host \\\"$($inv.Token): score=$($inv.Score), ratio=$($inv.Ratio)\\\"\\n}\\n\\n# Save results\\n$resultsPath = \\\"state/pulse_significance_scores.csv\\\"\\n$significanceResults | Sort-Object Score -Descending | Export-Csv -Path $resultsPath -NoTypeInformation\\nWrite-Host \\\"`nFull results saved to: $resultsPath\\\"\\n\\nreturn $invariants\",\r\n  \"file\": \"scripts/pulse-significance.ps1\"\r\n}","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774287697066}}
