{"type":"message","id":"c54b74bf","parentId":"d65acb55","timestamp":"2026-03-23T18:04:27.555Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see some issues:\n1. COMPRESSION-CAUSAL-DUALITY.md is only 3 bytes - it got corrupted/empty somehow\n2. TIC-EXPERIMENT.md is also 3 bytes - same issue\n3. The 10 pulses ran but most new file mutations failed because the files already existed\n\nThe 3-byte files are suspicious - that's probably just `{}` or `[]` or similar. Let me check what's in those files.","thinkingSignature":"297be4150b83640af7f9aa44518fda556d333f8a1166d671cb950fb81ccc96d1"},{"type":"text","text":"\nTwo research files look corrupted (3 bytes = empty content). Let me check:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q6rz6w0hr3p7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\research\\COMPRESSION-CAUSAL-DUALITY.md\" -Raw; echo \"---\"; Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\research\\TIC-EXPERIMENT.md\" -Raw","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":95707,"output":207,"cacheRead":13731,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109645,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774289061290}}
