KB\n- Plus 2 more\n\nThe pulse runs on a 30-min schedule (8am-11pm ET). It's generating real research docs on causal inference, compression, and cognitive architecture. The main remaining limitation is the LLM tends to revisit the same topics — that's a higher-level constraint of the goal/observation system, not a bug."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":99741,"output":529,"cacheRead":13731,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114001,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774289363703}}
