{"type":"message","id":"356d1c9c","parentId":"0408cc52","timestamp":"2026-03-23T18:57:42.121Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the second post is also live. Let me post the third one. And while I'm at it, let me think about the Modal/Spark endpoint issue.\n\nFor Modal/Spark: the container cold-starts and pulls the model. This takes a few minutes. Once the model is loaded, the endpoint should work. But the container might be shutting down between requests (scaledown_window=600 = 10 min). The T4 container is ephemeral — it spins down after 10 min of inactivity.\n\nThe real solution for a persistent endpoint would be to either:\n1. Remove the scaledown_window or set it very high\n\n\n2. Use a different Modal setup with persistent containers\n3. Accept the cold-start latency\n\nFor now, let me just note the status and move on. I should test the Spark endpoint again to see if it responds after the recent deploys, since each deployment creates a new container that needs to pull the model.","thinkingSignature":"0d67d5e1e374e8e0ad32b7b6d156b2de66a5268a3ffd1888b4f73fabc4bc7c27"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6sq8t95bq24b_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://toxzak-svg--spark-ollama-qwen-health.modal.run\" 2>&1; echo \"---\"; curl -s -X POST \"https://toxzak-svg--spark-ollama-qwen-generate.modal.run\" -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"prompt\":\"Return: OK\",\"model\":\"qwen2.5:7b\"}' 2>&1 | head -c 200","yieldMs":30000,"timeout":45}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":104481,"output":334,"cacheRead":13731,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118546,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774292253570}}
