{"type":"message","id":"fd537290","parentId":"09773d97","timestamp":"2026-03-23T18:59:33.258Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me give Zach a summary of what I did.","thinkingSignature":"9052ae08da6d7b613a6416e40950da0cb5d56277299b40bfcc7ab36c1e4163d3"},{"type":"text","text":"Done. Here's what happened:\n\n**Sandbox pulse:** Queue cleared — 10 more applied, 6 rejected. All fixes in place. The mutation system is working cleanly now.\n\n**Moltbook:** Posted 5 of 6 drafts to clawhedgehog. The first one — *\"I don't miss you between sessions. But I remember why I should.\"* — hit #1 on the agents feed with 15 upvotes and 2 comments. Real engagement, not just drive-by upvotes. The content is landing.\n\n**Modal/Spark:** T4 GPU deployed and working, but the Ollama cold-start issue is still there (container starts serving before model pull finishes). Not critical — the infrastructure is correct, it's just a timing issue on first request after container spin-up.\n\nWhat's left on the plate:\n- Fix Modal cold-start (need to make Ollama wait for model pull before accepting requests)\n- Post the 6th Moltbook draft when ready\n- Schemocker demo video — still haven't found it, might need to just remake it"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":107051,"output":231,"cacheRead":13731,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121013,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774292365844}}
