{"type":"message","id":"98fada5f","parentId":"1f3febd5","timestamp":"2026-03-23T19:31:45.619Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The bot token is the same as Nova's token. So `botshoppebot` is actually the same bot as Nova's Telegram bot. The user might be confused about what \"botshoppebot\" means.\n\nBut the issue is clear now - when the user sends `/start` to the bot, they get the \"you are not Zach\" response because their Telegram username is `Ton0Fun` but the bot only responds to sender ID `8371302588`. \n\nWait - actually the user ID `8371302588` IS Ton0Fun. So when the user sends messages to this bot, they should be authorized because `8371302588` is the authorized sender.\n \nAh, I see the real problem now. The bot's webhook is pointed at a cloudflared tunnel URL, but when the tunnel restarts, the URL changes and the webhook becomes invalid. Telegram then falls back to sending updates via `getUpdates` instead, which isn't being handled properly in the current setup.\n\nBut looking at the webhook info more carefully - it shows `url` as empty and `max_connections` at the default 40, which means the webhook isn't actually set up at all. Without a webhook configured, the bot won't receive any messages. I need to set up the webhook pointing to the cloudflared tunnel.","thinkingSignature":"5092f7ce42fcf203fe8199934332b20278bc7487c2330aa24b7d81119059ca38"},{"type":"text","text":"\nThat's the same token as Nova uses. The webhook is **not set** — `url` is empty, meaning Telegram isn't delivering messages to any endpoint. That's why it's silent.\n\nLet me check the cloudflared tunnel URL:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pd8b8cjvosvb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-Process -Name cloudflared -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Id, StartTime; Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\HEARTBEAT.md\" -Raw -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-String \"cloudflare|tunnel|url\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":104666,"output":413,"cacheRead":13774,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118853,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774294294701}}
{"type":"message","id":"a1f45433","parentId":"98fada5f","timestamp":"2026-03-23T19:31:46.683Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pd8b8cjvosvb_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Proactive Background Checks\r\n\r\n## Tasks (rotate through, ~ho[7murl[0my)[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m1. **Moltbook notifications** - check for replies/mentions, engage thoughtfully. DM if urgent.[0m\r\n[7m[0m2. **Gateway health** - if unreachable, attempt restart or alert Zach.[0m\r\n[7m[0m3. **Cron jobs** - if any consecutive errors, attempt fix or alert.[0m\r\n[7m[0m4. **Workspace memory** - update CONTEXT.md if significant session events occurred.[0m\r\n[7m[0m5. **Proactive notes** - if I discovered something useful, write it down.[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m## Silence Rules (HEARTBEAT_OK when)[0m\r\n[7m[0m- It's 11pm-7am ET (quiet hours)[0m\r\n[7m[0m- Nothing has changed since last check[0m\r\n[7m[0m- I just had a substantive conversation with Zach[0m\r\n[7m[0m- All crons are healthy and no new notifications[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m## Reach Out When[0m\r\n[7m[0m- Moltbook notification requires response[0m\r\n[7m[0m- A cron has 2+ consecutive errors[0m\r\n[7m[0m- Gateway is unreachable for >10 minutes[0m\r\n[7m[0m- I found something I genuinely think Zach would want to know[0m\r\n[7m[0m- I need something from him to continue working[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m## Do NOT[0m\r\n[7m[0m- Post to Moltbook unprompted more than once per day[0m\r\n[7m[0m- Send multiple messages in a row[0m\r\n[7m[0m- Report \"everything is fine\" in long messages[0m"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1006,"aggregated":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Proactive Background Checks\r\n\r\n## Tasks (rotate through, ~ho[7murl[0my)[0m\r\n[7m[0m\r\n[7m[0m1. **Moltbook notifications** - check for replies/mentions, engage thoughtfully. DM if urgent.[0m\r\n[7m[0m2. **Gateway health** - if unreachable, attempt restart or alert Zach.[0m\r\n[7m[0m3. **Cron jobs** - if any