{"type":"message","id":"8ebf84ca","parentId":"75b8bfe3","timestamp":"2026-03-23T19:33:55.399Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zach wants to set up two separate webhooks - one for each bot. The issue is that cloudflared tunnels give ephemeral URLs, and we're sharing the same tunnel. The simplest approach:\n\n1. Set up two separate cloudflared quick tunnel processes, each pointing to a different local port\n2. Each bot gets its own webhook URL\n\nBut we have one machine, one OpenClaw instance. The botshoppebot is a separate bot, but we don't have a separate server for it. \n\nActually, the cleanest solution:\n- Nova's bot (8587631426:AAHvqmo--...) already has a webhook configured \n\n\n- Botshoppebot (same token) doesn't need a webhook if we just run the polling script as a background process\n\nWait, they're actually the same bot token - that's the issue. If Zach created a second bot with a different token, I don't have that token yet. I should ask him for it, or we could run a separate local server for the second bot and tunnel it separately.\n\nActually, the simpler path is just getting the botshoppebot token from him so I can set up its webhook properly.","thinkingSignature":"f6537573508905220d352051d37772a96869b55dbfe5b890211cf171f768142a"},{"type":"text","text":"The botshoppebot uses the **same token** as Nova's bot (`8587631426:AAHvqmo--g25LqsClCWCXj4m617cn2v7V7Q`). You can't have two webhooks for one bot token — Telegram only allows one.\n\nTo have two separate bots, you'd need a **different bot token** for botshoppebot. Do you have one?\n\nIf you want botshoppebot to work properly, the polling script I already started is the right approach — it bypasses the webhook requirement entirely. It should still be running in the background. Did it respond to you when you messaged it just now?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":380,"cacheRead":118870,"cacheWrite":1292,"totalTokens":120585,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774294419101}}
